                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9785" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1476</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1089 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">拉夏贝尔缘何谢幕？——扩张“跃进”中的财务资源错配</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Why Did La Chapelle Fall? —— Misallocation of Financial Resources During Its Aggressive Expansion</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈智，王媛媛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东工商学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆拉夏贝尔服饰股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">拉夏贝尔；扩张战略；财务资源错配</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">La Chapelle; Expansion Strategy; Mismatch of Financial Resources</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以拉夏贝尔为例，深入探讨其由于扩张战略中的财务资源错配而导致“谢幕”的内在逻辑。拉夏贝尔曾在时尚领域风光无限，其为了拓展市场，积极扩张，包括盲目增加门店数量、过度多元化品牌布局、滞后的线上转型以及高昂的运营成本等，但并未精准匹配财务资源与扩张的步伐，致使财务资源错配问题逐渐凸显，引发资金链断裂、高负债和盈利能力持续下滑等问题，经营困境加剧，公司陷入巨额亏损，被迫关闭大量门店、变卖资产，但仍未能扭转颓势。最终在多重压力下，让昔日巨头陷入困境，由“中国女装第一股”走向退市。通过对本案例的研究，引导学生分析公司战略决策与财务资源配置的关联性，帮助学生明晰公司扩张中财务资源合理规划的重要性，汲取经验教训，助力提升应对财务风险和商业决策的能力，最终推动公司健康发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study takes La Chapelle as an example to explore in depth the internal logic of its &quot;curtain call&quot; due to the mismatch of financial resources in its expansion strategy. La Chapelle once had great success in the fashion industry. In order to expand its market, it actively expanded, including blindly increasing the number of stores, excessively diversifying its brand layout, lagging online transformation, and high operating costs. However, it did not accurately match its financial resources with the pace of expansion, resulting in a gradual mismatch of financial resources. This led to problems such as a broken capital chain, high debt, and continuous decline in profitability. The company&#39;s operating difficulties intensified, and it was forced to close a large number of stores and sell assets, but it still failed to reverse its decline. Ultimately, under multiple pressures, the former giant fell into a predicament and went from being the &quot;first stock of Chinese women&#39;s clothing&quot; to delisting. Through the study of this case, guide students to analyze the correlation between company strategic decision-making and financial resource allocation, help them clarify the importance of reasonable planning of financial resources in company expansion, learn from experience and lessons, help improve their ability to deal with financial risks and business decisions, and ultimately promote the healthy development of the company.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务分析与投资决策》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源配置;盈利能力;偿债能力;财务风险;资本结构</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
